Properties.Caption: Просмотр парных проводок районов
Properties.Tag: Select Case When Max([EX_DT_CT].[FLAGS] & 32)<>0 Then 'Y3' Else 'J3' End As [Тип документа проводки], [K_DIST].[CDIST] As [Район], [EX_DT_CT].[DBN] As [Дата проводки], Rtrim([K_EX_OP].[CEX_OP]) As [Операция проводки], [EX_DT_CT].[NUM] As [Номер], [K_BS_DT].[CBS] As [Балансовый счет дебета], [K_BS_CT].[CBS] As [Балансовый счет кредита], [EX_DT_CT].[PBK_DT] As [ПБК дебета], [EX_DT_CT].[PBK_CT] As [ПБК кредита], Sum([EX_DT_CT].[SUMM]) As [Сумма] From ((((((([EX_DT_CT] With (NoLock) Inner Join [EX_NUM] With (NoLock) On ([EX_DT_CT].[EX_NUMID]=[EX_NUM].[EX_NUMID])) Inner Join [K_DIST] With (NoLock) On ([EX_NUM].[K_DISTID]=[K_DIST].[K_DISTID])) Inner Join [K_EX_OP] With (NoLock) On ([EX_DT_CT].[K_EX_OPID]=[K_EX_OP].[K_EX_OPID])) Left Join [K_BS] As [K_BS_DT] With (NoLock) On ([EX_DT_CT].[K_BSID_DT]=[K_BS_DT].[K_BSID])) Left Join [K_BS] As [K_BS_CT] With (NoLock) On ([EX_DT_CT].[K_BSID_CT]=[K_BS_CT].[K_BSID])) Left Join [K_TD] As [K_TD_DT] With (NoLock) On ([EX_DT_CT].[K_TDID_DT]=[K_TD_DT].[K_TDID])) Left Join [K_TD] As [K_TD_CT] With (NoLock) On ([EX_DT_CT].[K_TDID_CT]=[K_TD_CT].[K_TDID])) Where [K_DIST].[CDIST]<>'30' And [K_DIST].[CDIST] Like GetCDIST() And |0 Group by [EX_DT_CT].[EX_NUMID], [K_DIST].[CDIST], [EX_DT_CT].[DBN], Rtrim([K_EX_OP].[CEX_OP]), [EX_DT_CT].[NUM], [K_BS_DT].[CBS], [K_BS_CT].[CBS], [EX_DT_CT].[PBK_DT], [EX_DT_CT].[PBK_CT] Order by |1
Properties.Name: Просмотр парных проводок районов
Тип документа проводки
